1,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"人之將死 其言也善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9203aab0921fd80196ed0bf305fb2c56f802fb13","tid":1684061,"uid":274732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"黃店冇呢回事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcb1fe03d3217bf714c2078b639184bb15df11d","tid":1684061,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:58:24.000Z","msg":"我驚今年聖誕節冇聖誕氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想體驗一吓冇聖誕節嘅香港，好有新鮮感，你咪繼續宵禁囉，好似要人怕你咁，條街夜晚九點本來就要咁靜先健康，如果西方呢個鐘數好多野都關晒門啦，係香港租金高先要開咁夜賺到盡，咩不夜天都係奴隸生活自欺欺人嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98070435eda13dc2ef90baa5c2f787de21677b46","tid":1684061,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"一向都講黨鐵提早收=宵禁<br />\n唔好同我地講,同你事頭婆講先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff33ee89c8724add454322112ae24dfdd14bc0","tid":1684061,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0235acd076d710aff94cd7a3529f7f6595b0c724","tid":1684061,"uid":57993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"多謝黑警"},{"pid":"9a7b03aa32d878e3103835637dc20429457f8758","tid":1684061,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=743b3aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}